### GetTBProfileStringFileKeys-获取本地数据中指定块名下所有键名集合 

```cpp
Bool GetTBProfileStringFileKeys(String strPath, String section, ArrayRef<String> keys)
```

**说明：**

> 获取本地数据中指定块名下所有键名集合。

**参数：**

| 参数名 | 类型 | 说明 |
| ------ | ---- | ---- |
| strPath    | String | 文件路径 |
| section    | String | 块名 |
| keys | ArrayRef&lt;string&gt; | 指定块名下键名集合 |

**返回值：**

| 类型 | 说明 |
| ---- | ---- |
| Bool | 获取成功返回True，获取失败返回False |

**示例：**

```cpp
Events
    OnInit()
    {
        Array<String> sections;
        Bool ret = GetTBProfileStringFileSections("D:\\traderApi.ini", sections);
        Print("GetTBProfileStringFileSections:" + IIFString(ret, "True", "False") + "," + TextArray(sections));
        Integer i;
        For i = 0 To GetArraySize(sections) - 1
        {
            Array<String> keys;
            ret = GetTBProfileStringFileKeys("D:\\traderApi.ini", sections[i], keys);
            Print("GetTBProfileStringFileKeys:" + IIFString(ret, "True", "False") + "," + TextArray(keys));
        }
    }
```

